in Poll SCM also we need to specify the intervalsa
at which the build is going to run.

But this is used in accordance with Remote repo

This job will be triggered when a new code is pushed towards our
github account.
This will be checked every 2 minutes by our 
PollSCM H/2 * * * *

If there is a new code in there,it will trigger.

if there are no push on our github,the build will not trigger



IMP - 
GitHub hook trigger for GITScm polling

Here the jenkins job will build whenever there is a new code pushed 
onto github,for this we need jenkins running on public IP 
Jenkins on aws or Azure can achieve this
